585
00:53:02,262 --> 00:53:05,222
Because I'm sane, Mrs. Barclay. Sane and rational.

586
00:53:07,350 --> 00:53:09,185
All right. All right.

587
00:53:09,269 --> 00:53:10,311
Do you remember what you said

588
00:53:10,395 --> 00:53:11,604
