631
01:00:23,411 --> 01:00:26,997
No fucking way. You got me into this, you get me out.

632
01:00:28,708 --> 01:00:30,375
I can't do that, Chucky.

633
01:00:30,460 --> 01:00:31,752
Why not?

634
01:00:32,128 --> 01:00:34,379
Because you're an abomination,

635
01:00:35,590 --> 01:00:37,799
an outrage against nature.

636
01:00:38,426 --> 01:00:42,888
You perverted everything I've taught you and used it for evil.

637
01:00:42,972 --> 01:00:44,765
And you have to be stopped.

638
01:00:48,603 --> 01:00:51,480
You know, I thought something like this might happen.

639
01:00:51,564 --> 01:00:53,231
That's why I prepared for it.

640
01:00:53,316 --> 01:00:54,816
What are you talking about?

641
01:00:55,401 --> 01:00:57,527
Your own personal mojo, doc.

642
01:00:58,905 --> 01:00:59,946
Give me that.

643
01:01:00,031 --> 01:01:02,240
Sure. How do you want it? Broken leg?

644
01:01:05,745 --> 01:01:09,873
Shouldn't tell your customers where you hide things like this, John.

645
01:01:09,957 --> 01:01:12,334
Gets you in trouble every time.

646
01:01:12,418 --> 01:01:14,961
Now how do I get out of this body?

647
01:01:15,046 --> 01:01:17,005
No, I won't tell you.

648
01:01:17,090 --> 01:01:18,090
Yeah?

649
01:01:20,593 --> 01:01:24,221
Tell me or die, John. Your choice.

650
01:01:24,305 --> 01:01:26,473
No, I'll tell you.

651
01:01:28,935 --> 01:01:32,229
You have to transfer your soul out of the doll

652
01:01:32,313 --> 01:01:36,400
into that of the first human being you revealed your true self to.

653
01:01:36,818 --> 01:01:41,154
You mean the first person I let in on the fact that I was really alive?

654
01:01:43,574 --> 01:01:46,493
I don't believe it. I just don't believe it.

655
01:01:46,577 --> 01:01:50,706
The first person I let in on my little secret was a six-year-old kid.

656
01:01:50,790 --> 01:01:53,208
