- What?

664
01:02:52,143 --> 01:02:54,436
Must save the boy. Must...

665
01:02:57,440 --> 01:02:59,232
Must get his soul

666
01:03:00,276 --> 01:03:03,069
into him like he got into doll.

667
01:03:03,488 --> 01:03:04,571
What?

668
01:03:05,239 --> 01:03:08,575
You must stop him before he can say the chant.

669
01:03:09,327 --> 01:03:12,037
Kill him before he can say it.

670
01:03:12,371 --> 01:03:13,872
But how? How?

671
01:03:14,791 --> 01:03:18,919
The heart. His heart is almost human.

672
01:03:21,422 --> 01:03:24,591
It's the only way. Through the heart.

673
01:03:42,568 --> 01:03:46,404
Help me! Help me! Dr. Ardmore, Chucky's here!

674
01:03:56,582 --> 01:04:01,002
Help me! He's coming to kill me! He's here. Chucky's here.

675
01:04:01,087 --> 01:04:02,963
I don't see anybody.

676
01:04:04,590 --> 01:04:07,050
But, Doctor, Chucky's here,

677
01:04:07,134 --> 01:04:09,302
and he's going to kill me.

678
01:04:12,598 --> 01:04:16,768
But Chucky is here, and he's going to kill me!

679
01:04:20,273 --> 01:04:22,691
He's going to kill me.

