01:15:10,422 --> 01:15:11,672
Andy!

745
01:15:11,757 --> 01:15:13,174
Please! Now!

746
01:15:25,103 --> 01:15:27,021
Andy, no, please.

747
01:15:28,190 --> 01:15:30,691
We're friends to the end. Remember?

748
01:15:31,109 --> 01:15:34,237
This is the end, friend.

749
01:16:18,865 --> 01:16:20,283
Oh, my baby.

