01:16:20,367 --> 01:16:22,159
MIKE: Karen? Andy?

751
01:16:22,703 --> 01:16:24,203
You all right?

752
01:16:31,545 --> 01:16:33,129
Andy, go get me the first-aid kit

753
01:16:33,213 --> 01:16:35,256
under the kitchen sink really fast. Okay?

754
01:16:35,340 --> 01:16:36,424
